Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:07.87,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:17.11,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:20.37,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:21.59,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.59,0:00:23.61,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.91,0:00:28.24,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Beer, beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.24,0:00:30.08,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:31.58,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:34.01,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna, it's cramped!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:34.26,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting cramped here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:35.00,Main-Top,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:10.63,Main,Realtor,0000,0000,0000,,A three bedroom apartment, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:14.15,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. As close to this \Narea as possible please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:15.52,Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:16.77,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:18.14,Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.14,0:02:19.40,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:20.77,Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:22.15,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:25.03,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly, there's not much \Ndifference between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.03,0:02:29.19,Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, the roof of this \Nproperty is a communal space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:30.03,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:35.18,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,The sky's so vast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:36.75,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,It feels nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:38.48,Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:43.51,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.51,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, time to start moving preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:50.23,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,First, we clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.52,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:55.14,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning, cleaning, la la la.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:58.78,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,Beat the dust and crush it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:02:59.71,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Weird song.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:01.90,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,Leave no dust or trash behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:04.32,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,Death to the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:07.96,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,now clean, clean everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:07.96,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:13.53,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tohru, do you like being clean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:17.98,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose so. I like bathing \Nand brushing my teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.98,0:03:21.55,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Brushing your teeth? Do you have \Na dragon-sized toothbrush?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:24.40,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, I use my claws to scrape out the bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:26.38,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Bugs?! Not bacteria?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:29.61,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they're so small I never notice them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:31.84,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Must be hard having a huge body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:34.59,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I went through a lot of trouble \Nsearching for places to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:37.60,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, figures. What kind \Nof places did you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:39.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes caves,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:40.61,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,sometimes ruins,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:42.23,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,sometimes mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:44.97,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've even slept up in the sky a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:46.24,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a migratory bird?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:49.49,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I guess you could \Nlive anywhere in that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:51.87,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:55.38,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I stayed in one place too long \Nhumans would soon start coming around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:56.44,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,They were so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:58.37,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You were like a rare monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:03.51,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,So not only did my body keep getting dirty, \NI had a hard time bathing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:04.83,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:07.56,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,When we had no other choice, \Nwe'd lick each other clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:08.21,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:09.71,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna and I did that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:12.58,Main-Top,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's naughty by human standards!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:13.64,sign_5998_62__They_were_actua,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,*They were actually in dragon form
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:13.64,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:17.14,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, most other dragons \Ndon't even care about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:19.70,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,We don't get sick or unhealthy either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:22.25,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I'm kind of jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:23.61,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.61,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi, you're sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:28.72,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You leave beer cans scattered about,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:31.12,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,you leave your clothes lying \Nwhere you took them off...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:32.56,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:34.87,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's one of the nice \Nthings about living alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:37.87,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you keep books arranged out of order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:40.07,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's just being too picky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.15,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:43.91,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. I'll overlook the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.91,0:04:46.35,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,But please clean up your trash and clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:47.88,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,This is my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:50.66,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You can't. Because Kanna \Nwill pick up those habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:52.10,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:56.23,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,My father must have felt this way \Nwhen my mother yelled at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:04:59.48,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Still, Tohru,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:04.73,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I keep doing that by accident because I'm \Nhappy you're here to clean it up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:05.23,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:09.71,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's a piece of a cake for \Na mighty dragon, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:10.86,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:14.32,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,So please keep helping out, okay, Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:19.45,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! With pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:20.08,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Simple-gon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:22.33,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Scoundrel Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:26.02,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, next up's packing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:29.74,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Though, nearly all of it is \Nmy personal belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:31.25,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:34.36,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, please ask anything of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:36.34,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:48.02,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanna. Pack properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:50.03,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi, so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:54.55,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,These dead-fish eyes are to die for!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:55.99,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru, you're a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:58.50,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What are you slacking off over?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:04.41,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this was still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:08.31,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:09.51,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:21.72,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:25.02,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is this yours, Miss Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:26.67,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It is, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:28.28,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Please try it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.85,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you in a maid outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:31.69,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:34.87,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But you bought it \Nintending to wear it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:38.19,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I got my arms into it and then \Ndespaired at how bad I looked in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:40.05,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm not wearing it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.40,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Then would you mind if I wear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:46.89,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:48.33,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:50.82,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:58.02,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru, so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.80,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think it looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:03.78,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.18,0:07:09.88,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Still, your clothes are bit \Ntoo tight in the chest for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:11.78,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That said...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:15.24,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really a D?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:17.12,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a D among dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:22.87,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:24.54,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.92,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:29.04,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Bath, bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:30.01,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:35.21,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone know what happened to the towels \Nand change of clothes in the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:37.97,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I put them away properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:38.72,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:39.72,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:44.26,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Which box has the clothes and towels?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:47.65,Main,Movers,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:50.44,Main,Movers,0000,0000,0000,,Sansan Moving Service!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:52.31,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.95,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:09.04,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's decide how to use the rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.04,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,This will be the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:13.29,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,This will be for the PC and books.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:15.80,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,This will be my bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:18.05,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,And this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:21.71,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,will be the room you two share.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:22.95,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:24.61,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Our room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:27.13,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You two can use it however you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:29.77,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:48.75,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,A new life, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:52.02,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I wash your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:54.53,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:57.88,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You like it when I make things clean, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:09:00.38,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, that's your angle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:02.53,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,All right, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:03.63,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.39,0:09:10.93,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,By the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.93,0:09:11.65,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:15.40,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it easier to wash \Nyour body in that form?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:19.40,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is, but it's a little limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:23.41,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, there are a lot of \Nrules in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:27.01,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a little stifling to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:30.83,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like having a human form?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:33.48,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:38.47,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is its own thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:41.72,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:48.38,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:50.32,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru, wash me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:51.75,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:52.89,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Cramped, it's cramped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:18.22,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:24.56,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:27.33,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:32.30,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:33.10,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.10,0:10:35.49,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wash your body as thanks for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:35.98,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:37.55,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Over here, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:38.82,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:48.80,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:51.37,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like I'm washing a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.37,0:10:55.50,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:57.90,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:14.90,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:17.21,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,This is my old apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:20.90,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, I screwed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:25.91,sign_16394_187_Episode_3,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 3
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:25.91,sign_16394_188_Start_of_a_New_L,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Start of a New Life! (That Doesn't Go Well, Of Course)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:44.60,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru, you're too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:45.25,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.26,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:52.35,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see me as a loud person?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:53.95,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:56.71,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi, does your hangover hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:57.62,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:00.69,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I can't believe it's \Nlike this on my day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:04.32,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,The noise is coming from the neighboring \Napartments and the floor above us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:06.19,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I go make a complaint?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:09.94,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, could you, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:12.87,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure not to let your horns stick out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:14.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:17.61,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,If they won't listen after I speak to them, \NI'll murder, destroy, and pulverize them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:18.46,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:21.47,sign_17706_204_Sasakibe,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sasakibe
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:21.47,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start with Ms. Sasakibe on our right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:23.84,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:25.45,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:27.61,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're from next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.80,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tohru. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:32.09,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. Did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:36.69,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we heard loud noises and they've \Nbeen bothering us, so I came over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:38.35,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,My, was it that loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:39.97,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:41.11,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:41.94,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.72,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:50.53,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Here, let me share some.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:52.41,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,They're stewed rapeseed blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:54.25,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:57.46,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies, but could you please \Nbe more mindful of the noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:58.28,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:03.46,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,How does she make that \Nmuch noise making this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:06.43,sign_17706_204_Sasakibe,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Yana
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:06.42,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Next is Mr. Yana on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:08.17,Main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm playing music.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:09.57,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Music?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.18,Main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, want to listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:13.18,Rar,,0000,0000,0000,,Rar
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:20.44,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice sounds like Hades \Nis crushing Hercules.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:23.69,Main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What a phrase! I'm taking it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:26.55,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, please try to keep the volume down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:27.26,Main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:30.24,sign_19358_232_Soune,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Soune
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:30.24,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Last is Mr. Soune on the floor above.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:32.74,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm using a drill for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:34.06,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,A drill?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:36.61,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm making hand-carved wooden ornaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:38.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it a gorilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:40.20,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:44.05,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, one of us is \Nsuffering from a hangover,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:45.55,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,so please try to keep the noise down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:46.63,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:50.14,Main,Sasakibe,0000,0000,0000,,You're the loud one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:51.74,Main-Top,Yana,0000,0000,0000,,You're the loud one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.07,0:13:52.96,Main,Soune,0000,0000,0000,,No, you two are being loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:54.96,Main,Sasakibe,0000,0000,0000,,The loud one is the one calling people loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:57.09,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.55,0:13:59.05,Main,Sasakibe,0000,0000,0000,,That drilling is too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:00.80,Main,Soune,0000,0000,0000,,That death metal voice is too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:02.30,Main,Yana,0000,0000,0000,,That strange noise is too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.88,Main,Sasakibe,0000,0000,0000,,That's cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:04.56,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:07.06,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Your voices are being too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:08.77,Main,Three,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:12.40,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Humans keep making the same mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:14.15,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,They're beyond help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:16.27,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:19.21,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Um, may I have a word here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:25.62,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What bothers us the most is having others \Nbe loud when we'd like some quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:30.22,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't we organize the times we \Ndon't want each other making noise,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:32.81,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,and make a schedule?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:37.01,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,If there are still times that don't \Nwork out, then we can use earplugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:40.51,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right with that, Miss Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.51,0:14:44.09,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,They're all creatures that haven't learned \Nanything since they evolved from apes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:46.12,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That goes for me, too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:50.27,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway, I usually wouldn't \Nmind if I weren't hung over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:53.44,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's only natural\Nto cause some bother
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:55.78,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,to others when people go about their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:14:57.55,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Especially so if they're neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.93,0:15:00.16,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you're too kindhearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:01.75,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:06.66,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't like it if it \Nwere too quiet either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:14.70,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to rest a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:15.77,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:36.77,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Am I loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:40.53,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:43.38,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Does it bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:48.54,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult to give a precise \Nanswer to that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:52.50,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.19,0:15:56.80,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I think a life like this is acceptable, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:06.52,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sleeping now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:10.26,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Then I will, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:19.83,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:51.74,sign_24204_283_Soon_the_cherry_,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, thank you for your hard work. \N\NSoon the cherry blossoms will be upon us again this year.\NSo with regards to that, we'd like to follow up on last year\N and host a flower viewing party for company staff.\NPlease organize a list of those who wish to attend \Nwithin each team and deliver it to General Manager Furukawa. Please try to attend if possible.\NThe time and location are in the attached file.\N\NThat is all, thank you.\N\NGeneral Manager Furukawa
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:51.74,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What should I do about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:54.32,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like the consideration that \Nhas to be shown when rank's dropped,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:56.20,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,and not being able to order certain liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:57.73,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Straight to the point, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:01.44,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then why not create \Nan excuse to refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:02.95,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,An excuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:05.70,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,A party?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:09.13,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I was talking to Takiya-kun \Nabout gathering here at this apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:11.71,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,as an excuse to turn down my \Ncompany's flower viewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:13.67,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're inviting him here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:17.21,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't make that \Nface now. He's a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:21.85,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, all right. I'll put up with that then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:22.72,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Put up with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:25.22,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,In return, can I call \Nsome of my friends, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:28.08,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Friends? Like from the shopping district?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.42,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:29.85,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.85,0:17:31.00,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:33.13,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,They're all well-behaved dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:35.07,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I'm only worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:37.06,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:38.57,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:40.11,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.11,0:17:42.29,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:43.87,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not welcome at all, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:47.37,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,You must be Kanna-chan. Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:48.98,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:50.60,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Nice goth-loli.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:53.04,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Where are your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:54.62,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,They should be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:57.46,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:01.53,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait one moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:06.22,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fafnir, please arrange yourself \Nlike in the picture I sent over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:07.76,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:15.85,Main-Top,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,This world is full of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:16.24,sign_26241_325_Fafnir,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(938,1)}Fafnir
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:18.69,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Makes me want to end it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:20.12,sign_26360_327_Hostility,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Hostility
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:22.99,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi, this is Mr. Fafnir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:23.83,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:24.95,Main-Top,K,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:33.88,sign_26473_329_It_s_a_pleasure_,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure to meet you. \NIt's an honor to make your acquaintance. \NI'm honored. \NYour friend has been very kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:28.25,Main-Top,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kobayashi from Jigokumeguri \NSystem Engineering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.51,0:18:28.07,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,That's a polite social greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:29.80,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Polite social greeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:31.25,Main-Top,K,0000,0000,0000,,I've been living with Tohru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:33.88,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,A magic set of words that allows \Neven shy people to greet others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:33.88,Main-Top,K,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we can get along well in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:35.34,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:37.84,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I got a really hostile \Nfeeling from him just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:41.38,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he may have a slight \Ndislike for humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:45.92,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,He's a cursed dragon who's been guarding his \Ntreasure in a cave since ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:46.88,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,He's a shut-in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:49.82,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You invited more?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:51.05,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:52.90,sign_27146_348_MISSING,,0000,0000,0000,,Unacceptable
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:54.75,Main,Lucoa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:56.48,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, it's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:59.41,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi, this is Miss Quetzalcoatl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:02.49,sign_27323_349_Quetzalcoatl,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(777,1)}Quetzalcoatl
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:02.48,Main-Top,L,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. Lucoa is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.48,0:19:05.48,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Why are all dragons so huge?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:06.39,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:07.71,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:10.12,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. I'm Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:12.24,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:16.07,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Um, did you walk here in that outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:17.12,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:19.71,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Your outfit is kind of slutty, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:20.75,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:38.56,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,Care to try?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:43.82,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,Once you cut into them, back away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:44.78,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:47.44,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you can't run in while \Nhe's doing that move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:49.62,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,Try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:50.67,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:51.83,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,Good job defeating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:54.36,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,Now, ignore that treasure chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:58.30,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,That was a mimic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:00.05,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:03.53,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,He's hooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.59,0:20:09.92,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru hardly ever used to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:12.68,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Must be thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:14.85,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a normal human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:18.62,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,That girl's never had \Nanything normal before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.62,0:20:21.69,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Not just her, but her friends as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:23.70,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Lucoa-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:26.86,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful to Tohru, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:31.62,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't use to smile much myself either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:33.98,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'll never say it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:36.99,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Food's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:37.99,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.37,0:20:39.74,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's eat then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:41.04,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Can you drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:42.29,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.29,0:20:46.04,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I can, but at least let me check \Nit for curses first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:46.80,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Curses?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:51.13,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago Ms. Lucoa was driven out of \Nher seat as a goddess thanks to liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:53.77,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,She was forced to drink liquor \Nher comrade had cursed,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:56.02,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,and in her drunken stupor she \Nwent to her little sister and—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:58.97,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.46,0:21:02.07,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Dragons don't have very \Ngood pasts, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:04.31,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.31,0:21:06.56,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to butlers, \NI fancy middle-aged ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:07.93,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,This is out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:09.20,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! You'll make me screw up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:12.37,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, lately young, handsome,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:14.83,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,but devilish butlers have been pretty \Ngood in their own way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.90,0:21:14.83,Main-Top,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,I said stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:19.05,Main-Top,K,0000,0000,0000,,Not having that wisdom of life aura \Nmeans they're out! Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.07,0:21:17.65,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,She's a completely different \Nperson when drunk, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:18.58,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:21.87,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you woman there! Become a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:23.27,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.27,0:21:24.59,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru, you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:26.14,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I already am one, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:29.51,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you before, that's just cosplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:31.46,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got complaints, then strip!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:34.37,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, what's with all of \Nyou and your absurd chests?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.74,0:21:32.62,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:35.01,Main-Top,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,Fafnir-dono! We must avert our eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:36.62,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you share some with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:37.26,Main-Top,F,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:38.63,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,But that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:39.36,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:40.58,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't, then strip!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:52.57,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, yeah, some people \Nmove their bodies to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:27.84,Next Episode,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,226)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.74,0:23:29.06,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,Fafnir-dono, ignore that treasure chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.76,0:23:31.08,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,That's a mimic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.08,0:23:33.06,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that chest is also—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.06,0:23:34.89,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,That was a mimic, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:37.73,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you reflexively \Ngo after all the chests?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:39.84,sign_33947_424_Episode_4,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(226,1)}Episode 4
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:39.84,sign_33947_425_Kanna_Goes_to_Sc,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(226,1)}Kanna Goes to School! (Not That She Needs To)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.73,0:23:38.65,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,It's my nature.
